The following OPTi BIOS versions are described here, in this order:

  - 586     586VHP Pentium     (586VHP)
  - 386+486 495XLC             (495xlc)
  - 486     SCWB2 Single-Chip  (801)
  - 386+486 SLC Super-Low-Cost (495slc)
  - 386+486 DxSC Single-Chip   (499)
  - 386+486 LCWB Low-Cost      (495sx)
  - 386+486 DxWB Single-Chip   (498)
  - 386/486 DxPI Single-Chip   (496+497)
  - 386/486 WriteBack cache    (391,491,493,495)
  - 386/486 WriteThru cache    (381,481)
  - 386SX   SxWB WriteBack     (291)
  - 386SX   SxPI Single-Chip   (283)
  - 386SX   SxPW PostWrite     (281)

Note: See legend at bottom for Turbo/LED (8042) abbreviations.

Note: Except where noted otherwise, WriteBack Cache designs
      may omit Dirty-Bits.

==============================================================================

-----------------------------------------------
OPTi 586VHP  586 ("Pentium") Chipset
-----------------------------------------------


Filename   Port      Description  586VHP
--------   -------   ---------------------------------------------------------
V076B503   OPTI503   586 ("Pentium"), default WriteThru (DataExpert)
V076B504   OPTI504   586 ("Pentium"), default WriteBack


